data.name: OTPLabel.Text
data.value: A 5 digit One-Time-Pin has been sent to your mobile number ending with Input the OTP below to proceed with Login. The OTP has a expiry time of 120 seconds. To prevent brute-force attacks, failing your 3 total Login attempts will result in permanent lockout. You can use the Resend button to request for a new OTP to be sent to you.
